@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 로그인
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@graphify.dev",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### GET /watchlist/me — 성공
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/watchlist/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /watchlist/me — 실패 (미인증)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/watchlist/me

###

### POST /watchlist/me — 성공
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/watchlist/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": 6
}

###

### DELETE /watchlist/me/{companyId} — 성공
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/watchlist/me/6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /companies/compare — 성공
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies/compare?ids=1,2,3&basis=INVESTMENT
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /companies/compare — 실패 (4개 초과)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies/compare?ids=1,2,3,4&basis=INVESTMENT
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
